text: "I Told You So" is a song by American singer Carrie Underwood from her second studio album, Carnival Ride (2007). ==Music video== It premiered on CMT on February 20, 2009. The music video reached number 1 on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for the week of May 22, 2009. ==References== Category:2007 songs Category:Carrie Underwood songs
